M5T5mHbs6aKaXeOQ","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"189","text":"Tricúspide: regurgitación, V pico","guid":"x2q8EwmWTb2Gew1Br5lljw","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"189","text":"PAPS estimada","guid":"A_jSMO2aTsKs0Hr5cusezA","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"189","text":"Pericardio: derrame sí/no","guid":"hb6xw2wDQi6f0JAUkbROAw","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"189","text":"VCI: diámetro + colapso","guid":"ocuHA-vWTIuFB1U9ep0dIw","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"189","text":"Aorta: raíz, ascendente, cayado, descendente","guid":"4mYTVFyHTny2XQdecKqUYw","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"189","text":"Conclusión 3 líneas máximo","guid":"qulvFSk0SNuaAG4R7qS-RQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"204","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas","guid":"KEimroVMQLGtupy9B8O10A","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"VENTANA DIFÍCIL es la regla en adulto mayor","guid":"kkyLAGcTR1WMuSSJhj-Ynw","children":[{"id":"206","parent":"205","text":"Cifoescoliosis, EPOC, hiperinsuflación, mamas grandes","guid":"GX11hj-7QSaJI2lo1ArNGg","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"205","text":"Rescate: insistir subcostal + ecocontraste","guid":"xELJVKKzSFC0Qa_bt7MR4g","children":[]}]},{"id":"208","parent":"204","text":"ESCLEROSIS aórtica ≠ estenosis","guid":"cHWpXZ_FSFaENlIPxFxw1g","children":[{"id":"209","parent":"208","text":"Engrosamiento sin gradiente (V <2.5 m/s, gradiente <20 mmHg)","guid":"6298Q1pzRTuwCPd698ROQA","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"208","text":"Hallazgo degenerativo en >70a","guid":"7rWLzP2qTueuRkEWU5Xd0g","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"208","text":"Reportar sin alarmar","guid":"0CljBDq6QPSFN9Aaip_KPw","children":[]}]},{"id":"212","parent":"204","text":"IM FUNCIONAL por dilatación anular","guid":"wRynocKRTvWl7_WieeDXyQ","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"Frecuente en FA crónica","guid":"AxTv6giDSfi9Ytp9dSD3EQ","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"Grado leve-moderado","guid":"XGhrpjOGT8ylJ30oUB3zfg","children":[]},{"id":"215","pa